parameters:
This morning, after a night of incredibly strong winds and
rain, the weather cleared completely without a trace.

The sky-high towering clouds and the vast, expansive sea,
along with the warm, shining sunlight, seem to be
telling the story of the upcoming summer.

Now, because the temperature difference is a bit extreme,
it's tough to just jump into the sea carelessly...
Hmm, if I have the chance, I'd like to come back again.
With such sentimental thoughts, I made my way to the pier.
It feels I'm missing somthing really important...
I have my smartphone, wallet, and even a charger...
